---
// BLVSTACK wordmark — uses Λ (Greek capital Lambda, U+039B) as the stylized 'A'.
// It's a letter character so it inherits surrounding font weight/size cleanly.
// Screen readers see "BLVSTACK" via aria-label.
---
<span aria-label="BLVSTACK" style="white-space: nowrap;"
  ><span aria-hidden="true">BLVSTΛCK</span></span>
